Package: guile-avahi
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Guile 1.8 bindings for the Avahi library
 Guile-Avahi provides bindings for GNU Guile 1.8 of the Avahi client
 library.  Avahi itself is a mDNS/DNS-SD implementation that provides,
 among other things, service discovery and publication facilities.
 .
